    "description": "Gird up your dinosaur suit and challenge your friends to discover who is the one who is most in touch with their prehistoric side!<br><br>Compete against each other in a variety of minigames, add modifiers to change your gameplay experience, or go into our challenge mode with crazy wacky stages.<br><br><strong>[Grand Prix mode]</strong><br>Do you prefer a curated experience? Our fixed circuit feature features 5 stages specially picked for players to play!<br><br>For the players who prefer to experience the game via their own two claws, the custom circuit feature is available as well! <br><br><strong>[Modifiers]</strong><br>Dino Dash Party offers 9 modifiers to evolve the gameplay of our minigame stages! These modifiers are promised to add good chaotic fun to familiar stages. <br><br><strong>[Play with friends]</strong><br>Grab a controller and play with up to 3 other friends, either through local co-op or steam remote play! <br><br><i>Please note: This is a local multiplayer game and at least one controller is required to play the game.</i>",
